### Register
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "neo1",
  "email": "neo1@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

### Login (identity can be username or email)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "neo1",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

### Forgot password
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/auth/forgot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "neo1"
}

### Reset password (use debug_otp from /forgot response)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/auth/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identity": "neo1",
  "otp": "123456",
  "new_password": "NewPassw0rd!"
}
